The paper deals with secure communication in a multiple-antenna system, which is a topic that falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-categories. The use of beamforming techniques also suggests that the paper may belong to the networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) and systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions simulation results, indicating that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
